Test Assets (assets-private/ directory)

The assets-private/ directory contains test assets used for internal development and
parity testing with the PlayCanvas engine. These assets are NOT included in
public releases and must not be redistributed.

Sources and licenses:

  Models from Sketchfab (CC-BY-4.0):
    See individual .txt files alongside each model for attribution.

  Cubemap environment atlases, textures, HDRIs:
    Sourced from PlayCanvas engine examples for internal testing only.
    Original provenance and licenses may vary per asset.

For public/open-source distribution, substitute these with original assets
or confirmed CC-0/public domain alternatives.
